Job Description
Challenge requests, streamline the processes and contribute ideas about the information required in order to ensure that the value obtained is worthwhile.
Ensure all processes are complying with all the policies and keep risks under control.
Take responsibility for all risk & control issues, and successful delivery of assessment and remediation interventions in support of the strategic and operational HR Governance of the Bank.
Provide recommendations to drive exceptional business performance at country and functional level.
Contribute to the sustainability of HR Operations by creating robust processes.
